      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Dust your work surface with a generous sprinkling of <strong>flour</strong></p><p>Unwrap your <strong>puff pastry</strong> and roll it out to approx. 0.5cm thickness with a <strong>rolling pin </strong>and cut into<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>1 square per person</p><p>Add the <strong>pastry squares</strong> to the tray[s]<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>and score a 1cm border around the edge of the pastry with a knife</p><p>Crimp the borders with a fork and put the tray[s] in the oven for 15-20 min or until puffed up, golden and cooked through – these are your <strong>pie lids</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/RC1826Step-4-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/RC1826Step-4-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/RC1826Step-4-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
