            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/RC1826Step-4-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Whilst the pie lids are cooking, cut your <strong>Brussels sprouts</strong> in half lengthways</p><p>Add them to a separate baking tray with your <strong>balsamic vinegar</strong>, a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and give them a good mix up</p><p>Put the tray in the oven and cook for 15 min or until the sprouts are tender and slightly crispy – these are your <strong>balsamic roasted sprouts</strong></p><p>Reboil half a kettle</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/RC1826Step-5-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/RC1826Step-5-x400.jpg",
