    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Return the <strong>drained potato & carrot</strong> to a low heat and add a splash of <strong>milk</strong> and a knob of <strong>butter</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mash, then season generously with <strong>salt </strong>– this is your<strong> potato & carrot mash</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
