      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>creamy mushrooms</strong> with the <strong>potato & carrot</strong> <strong>mash</strong> and<strong> balsamic roasted sprouts</strong> to the side</p><p>Sit the<strong> pie lid</strong> over the creamy mushrooms</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
